<paragraph id="98D7A96F1A42D9478A58D04505E3C7F3" pageId="0" pageNumber="55">site 4: slide BUL-4-1; Site 7: slide BUL-7-6; site 10: slides BUL-10-2, BUL-10-5.</paragraph>
